Dialogue: 0,00:02:40.200,00:02:42.360,辉英,,0,0,0,,This is just subtracting two equalities.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.000,00:02:44.520,辉英,,0,0,0,,Both are true.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:45.720,00:02:49.720,辉英,,0,0,0,,And simply by linearity and the definition of ek,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.720,00:02:53.920,辉英,,0,0,0,,the left-hand side becomes d of ek plus 1.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.620,00:02:56.640,辉英,,0,0,0,,And the right-hand side,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:56.640,00:02:57.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,the b,
